SHORTCUTS
---------
Jump to sidebar - CTRL + 0
Jump back to code - ENTER
Edit multiple selection - ALT + F3
Select selected words on document - CTRL + D
Duplicate line - CTRL + SHIFT + D
Expand selection - CTRL + L
Move line up/down - CTRL + SHIFT + UP/DOWN
Select tag - CTRL + SHIFT + A
Join lines - CTRL + J
Remove tag (also ending) - CTRL + SHIFT + ; (NOTE: should switch to US keyb and ctrl+shift+รถ)

SHORTCUTS CUSTOMIZED
--------------------
Block comment - CTRL + ร


HTMLBeautify-plugin
-------------------
Beautify - CTRL + SHIFT + ALT + F
